name: convert
func:
msg.payload = (msg.payload.data[1] << 16) + msg.payload.data[0];

return msg;

name: collecting data
func:
msg = {
    trans_volume: flow.get("trans_volume"),
    driver_id: flow.get("driver_id"),
    driver_desc: flow.get("driver_desc"),
    driver_name: flow.get("driver_name"),
    vehicle_id   : flow.get("vehicle_id"),
    vehicle_desc : flow.get("vehicle_desc"),
    vehicle_name : flow.get("vehicle_name"),
    vehicle_number: flow.get("vehicle_number"),
}

return msg;
